---
// Services page
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Hair PRP Services">
  <section>
    <h1>Our PRP Hair Restoration Services</h1>
    <p>We offer specialized PRP treatments designed to combat hair loss and promote healthy hair growth.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>PRP Hair Treatment Packages</h2>

    <article>
      <h3>Basic PRP Session</h3>
      <p>Single PRP treatment session for mild hair thinning.</p>
      <p><strong>Price: AED 1,200</strong></p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h3>Standard Treatment Package</h3>
      <p>Package of 3 sessions spaced 4-6 weeks apart.</p>
      <p><strong>Price: AED 3,200</strong></p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h3>Premium Treatment Package</h3>
      <p>Comprehensive package of 6 sessions with follow-up care.</p>
      <p><strong>Price: AED 5,800</strong></p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Additional Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Hair Loss Consultation & Assessment</li>
      <li>Scalp Analysis</li>
      <li>Personalized Treatment Plans</li>
      <li>Post-Treatment Care Guidance</li>
      <li>Progress Monitoring</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <details>
      <summary>How does PRP therapy work?</summary>
      <p>PRP therapy uses your body's own platelets to stimulate hair follicles and promote growth.</p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>Is PRP treatment safe?</summary>
      <p>Yes, PRP is a safe, minimally invasive procedure with minimal side effects.</p>
    </details>

    <details>
      <summary>When will I see results?</summary>
      <p>Most patients begin to see results after 3-4 months of treatment.</p>
    </details>
  </section>
</Layout>